      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. Paired with a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential, the chassis provides exceptional feedback and turn-in precision. The rear subframe has been reinforced and the suspension bushings remain tight, ensuring this driver-focused machine handles high-G cornering with composure. Meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical integrity, this specimen is optimized for the technical driver.",
